description: The index seeks to target 75% of the float market capitalization (i.e., the amount of stock which is available for trading by the general public) of each Global Industry Classification Standard Industry Group (“GICS Industry Group”) within the S&P SmallCap 600 Index, using an ESG score as the defining characteristic. The fund will invest at least 80% of its total assets (but typically far more) in component securities of the index. It is non-diversified.
name: Xtrackers S&P SmallCap 600 ESG ETF
